Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Alice Keck Park Memorial Garden
Description: A pretty park with flowers and cute turtles! Great for picnics!

Name: East Beach
Description: An awesome place to watch the sunset with a view of beautiful palm trees and the pier!

Name: 1000 Steps Beach
Description: Beware, there are a lot of stairs! But the beautiful beach makes it worth it!

Name: Santa Barbara Downtown
Description: Very cute downtown area with a ton of shops!

Name: Goleta Beach Park
Description: A great beach to watch the sunset or take a stroll along the Goleta Pier!
